      "writtenOn": "2015-11-09T17:04:46Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "well, isn\u0027t it the same now? It either sends a command or does nothing - if there\u0027s no device to send to\nI\u0027m curious what useful could be done prior to this line if there\u0027s no device",
      "parentUuid": "d66b7268_0a80db62",
